### Đăng ký tài khoản
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Nguyen",
  "lastName": "Admin",
  "email": "admin@smarthub.local",
  "password": "Admin@1234"
}

### Đăng nhập
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@smarthub.local",
  "password": "Admin@1234"
}

### Lấy dữ liệu cảm biến (thay TOKEN bằng token từ login)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/sensors/latest
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Bật relay 0
POST http://localhost:3000/api/relays/0
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "state": true
}

### Lấy danh sách relay
GET http://localhost:3000/api/relays
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN